column2: "Me? I'm here supporting a higher up ARKS member who was kind of too hard to turn down."
"Since you started off as a rookie, you've been trying really hard. I think everyone expects a lot from you."
"I've been trying to keep up with everyone's expectations too, but it's really tiresome."
"I guess all I can do is do everything I can help out those in front of me..."
"I know you know that about me. But still I wonder why that old man Regius dragged me all the way out here?"
"Sorry I got caught up in thought. Anyways, <%me> don't let people's expectations get the best of you."
